title: Fakt Ladh Mhana (2011) Marathi Movie
description:
Fakta Ladh Mhana (2011)


StoryLine:

Fakta Ladh Mhana is a 2011 Marathi film starring Aniket Vishwasrao, Siddharth Jadhav, Sanjay Narvekar, Santosh Juvekar, Bharat Jadhav, Mahesh Manjarekar, Sachin Khedekar and Vaibhav Mangle.

The story revolves around a gang who consists of Tukaram (Bharat Jadhav), Westindies (Siddharth Jadhav), a dark guy, Kanphatya (Sanjay Narvekar), who has hearing problems, a Salim (Santosh Juvekar), Alex (Aniket Vishwasrao), an aggresive guy, Paani Cum a small boy and Baba Bhai (Mahesh Manjarekar) leader of the gang.
